rows.label: tlk000001_msg0001
rows.name:
Never thought I'd see the day you'd
be on the Uzushio with us, Rex.

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0002
rows.name:
Guess it just goes to show your skill
as a salvager is getting widely recognized.

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0003
rows.name: It makes me happy to see.

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0004
rows.name:
So, are you all set? We'll be setting
sail as soon as you're on board.

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0008
rows.name:
That's the spirit!
Alright then, hurry up and get on board!

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0009
rows.name:
This time we're heading for an unexplored
sea region. It's exciting, isn't it!

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0010
rows.name:
Well, maybe I shouldn't say it like this,
but you can always come back here.

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0011
rows.name: It's not like we're heading off to a battlefield.

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0012
rows.name:
And this isn't a final goodbye, so there's
no need to get all worked up.
